    Class Description

    a Request for the server to check existing of a certain entity by its primary keys Stores the data for the CheckExistsRequest that will be sent to the server from the client

    GetJoinedTablesWhereRequest

    a Request for the server to get images data Stores the data for the ImageRequest that will be sent to the server from the client

    RemoveRequest

    Request
    The base class for all Request types
    Response

    UpdateRequest
